------------------------------------------
d11 1
a11 6
* Download and install the PHP/Java Bridge base and the libraries. For
  example:

    rpm -i php-java-bridge-mono-x.y.z-1-i386.rpm

  On non-Linux OS start the .NET VM by double-clicking on MonoBridge.exe
d16 1
